
DataStreamer




Events
    TickEvent
    SignalEvent
    OrderEvent
    FillEvent

EventListener:
    TickEventListener -> uses strategy to place orders
    SignalEventListener -> uses portfolio
    OrderEventListener -> uses execution to do order..
    FillEventListener -> capture results..


